    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "We added the zeroize attribute to SecretKey in the latest blst crate (v0.3.1).  Let us know if that helps or if more should be done.\r\n```\r\n        #[derive(Default, Debug, Clone, Zeroize)]\r\n        #[zeroize(drop)]\r\n        pub struct SecretKey {\r\n            value: blst_scalar,\r\n        }\r\n```\r\n",
